	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm a lvl 3 bard just started not a twink the only equipment i have is a rusty long sword and now thanks to the bonechip quest in kaladim i have a tattered leather tunic. So here is my question is there a faster way to get money and get the regular leather or is this one of those things you have to beg for untile you hit lvl 16 or higher?<br><br><br>Thanks for your answers.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
