	   <tr><td colspan=2>Alright there's a better way to get your swiming up.  Just find a nice pond somewhere where you know you will be safe not matter what.  Next find a wall the u could run into forever and never get out of the water.  It helps to use a corner for this.  Next just aim yourself at the wall and put a rock on the forward key.  Leave and go to party, take a bath, drink a soda or something.  Now you come back and your swiming is maxed! Yay!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
