	   <tr><td colspan=2>If by 'ME NO EAT' you mean you use Jaxan's Jig o' Vigor whenever your stamina drops from hunger/thirst, then you should know that even if you sing Jaxan's constantly, being hungry or thirsty will eventually make you unable to regen HP naturally. Although you could just sing a regen song (most songs bards get are regen songs, not heal songs, there's a difference) it will lower your ability to regenerate hit points. Maybe I'm wrong, and if so I apologize, but I thought you might want to know<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
